# Shared Component Rules

## Promotion Policy

| Scope | Location |
|---|---|
| Used in 1 feature only | `features/<n>/components/` |
| Used in 2+ features | `components/shared/` |
| Base primitive (button/input/card) | `components/ui/` (shadcn) |
| Pure utility function | `lib/` |
| Shared type/interface | `types/` |

> Default: keep code in the feature. Promote only when reuse is confirmed.

## components/ui

- Shadcn/Radix primitives only
- Do not add business logic here
- Extend via `components/shared/`, not by modifying `ui/` directly

## components/shared

Organized by pattern type:
```
shared/
  badges/     # status/semantic badges
  cards/      # summary/info cards
  dialogs/    # confirm/action dialogs
  filters/    # search/filter toolkits
  navigation/ # back button, nav controls
  pagination/ # pagination widgets
  panels/     # loading/empty/error states
  table/      # data-table ecosystem
```

- Must not import from any `features/*`
- Must not contain feature-specific business rules
- Must be props-driven, no global state

## UI Conventions

- Mobile-first: critical actions must be reachable without hover
- Use `components/ui` before creating new primitives
- Use `components/shared` before duplicating pattern across features
